QuestData.Title: Prime the Cannons
QuestData.Description: The armory is lost to the traitors. All we have left are these few cannons with no ammunition.$B$BSoldier, I need you to recover cannonballs so we can get these things running.$B$BActually, one more cannon wouldn't hurt, either.
QuestData.LogDescription: Recover $1oa Ironcoat Cannonballs and $2oa Armory Cannon.
QuestData.CompletionText: I hope you're toting a cannon and some balls, soldier.
